                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "In a small bowl, combine the honey, soy sauce, sesame oil, garlic, ginger, and a pinch of salt and pepper."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Season the drumsticks with salt and pepper, taste and place in a Ziploc bag; pour the liquid mixture over all the pieces. Seal the bag, remove as much air as possible and marinade in the refrigerator for at least two hours (preferably overnight.) Do not discard the marinade!"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Preheat the oven to 425 degrees F."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Lay chicken on a foil or parchment-lined baking sheet."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Bake for approximately 35 minutes (basting every 10 minutes with the marinade) or until a thermometer inserted into the thickest part reads 165ºF."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
